You know what I realized afte rlooking at Stephen Hayes dojo site. His 
buisness is shady at best. 

To go to one of his seminars it costs $300. And supposing I was dumb 
enough to want to teach his stuff at a dojo I would have to buy the
 dvd on which class I want to teach, watch it, then send mor emoney to 
have a curriculum sent to me. 

http://www.skhquest.com/

Sorry to ressurect the whole Hayes thing, but god is there no decency.

Maikeru
